data.description: This beautiful 2222 Sq. Ft. Cortez Exterior Design A home has been meticulously updated and is a very well-maintained home by the current owners. This home comprises 2-Bedroom En-Suites that have both been extended; Powder Room; Great Room; Dining Room; Spacious Den, that could be easily turned into a 3rd bedroom; Grand Kitchen Island; Generous Walk-in Closet in Primary Suite; Primary Bath 42'' x 60'' Shower and Built-in Seat; Walk-in Closet in Bedroom 2 En-Suite; Separate Laundry Room; Deep 2-Car Garage (Extended 4-feet) w/Golf Cart Garage & Custom-made Storage Cabinets; ''Screened-In'' 192 sq. ft. of Covered Outdoor Living Space w/additional Covered patio ''bump-out'' that nearly triples the coverage under roof; and 9' & 11' Ceiling Heights throughout the home. The Garage has epoxy coat floors; Soft-water system; Sink; "Gorilla Racks"; and Custom-made Cabinets lining the entire side wall + the garage has been extended 4-feet. The home has been professionally landscaped - both front and back yards.  This home is situated on a very quiet street within Unit 2 of SaddleBrooke Ranch.
